Now, tomorrow, day after, and after that,

50:36.480 --> 50:38.400
we are going to have three more programs.

50:38.640 --> 50:40.960
Today, in a general way, I have spoken to you because

50:41.160 --> 50:43.680
they said "Just give introduction to Sahaja Yoga,

50:43.880 --> 50:44.920
what is Sahaja Yoga is",

50:45.120 --> 50:47.680
and that's how I told you that you cannot pay for it

50:47.880 --> 50:49.920
it is effortless, it is spontaneous,

50:50.120 --> 50:54.840
it's a living process and through the grace of God it works out.

50:55.040 --> 50:58.800
And by this happening you get your transformation.

50:59.000 --> 51:02.840
You become something else than what you are, in your awareness.

51:03.040 --> 51:05.120
You become a more powerful person

51:05.320 --> 51:08.120
a dynamic person, you start feeling another person.

51:08.320 --> 51:12.680
It's a fact. You can ask, somebody has come now

51:12.880 --> 51:15.360
all the way from Perth, and when he came to Me

51:15.560 --> 51:19.680
he was in a big problem because he had been to gurus, this thing,

51:19.880 --> 51:21.880
and he, he realized that he's made a mistake

51:22.080 --> 51:23.680
but nothing could rectify it.

51:23.880 --> 51:27.040
But now he's rectified and he could feel this cool breeze,

51:27.240 --> 51:29.760
actually on his head and all over.

51:29.960 --> 51:33.320
So, this is the thing one has to understand, that

51:33.520 --> 51:37.400
you must honestly ask for the truth,

51:37.640 --> 51:40.880
and not for something that is being told to you before.

51:41.080 --> 51:43.680
This is what it is, should happen to you,

51:43.880 --> 51:46.680
that has never happened before, and cannot happen

51:46.880 --> 51:49.400
through human effort. So, tomorrow,

51:49.640 --> 51:52.160
day after and after that, we have three more days.

51:52.360 --> 51:54.800
One day I will talk about chakras,

51:55.000 --> 51:57.520
tomorrow, and then about these three powers.

51:57.720 --> 52:01.560
And last day I'll tell you what is to be done after Self Realization

52:01.760 --> 52:04.720
how to keep it up, how your Spirit is your guru,

52:04.920 --> 52:07.880
and how he teaches through your vibratory awareness,

52:08.080 --> 52:10.520
how you understand what is right and what is wrong.

52:10.720 --> 52:14.000
I think that is how we'll space it out and we'll work it out.

52:14.200 --> 52:15.320
But today we should try

52:15.560 --> 52:18.280
to have the session of Self Realization also.

52:18.520 --> 52:21.680
It might be, might work out very well. May God bless you!

