so many points, you see, not easy to tell you all about it.

54:17.680 --> 54:20.680
But you will know each and everything about Kundalini,

54:20.880 --> 54:23.080
yourself you will be able to raise the Kundalini,

54:23.280 --> 54:26.080
you'll be able to give Realization to people and understand it

54:26.320 --> 54:28.520
