What is it?

55:49.080 --> 55:53.120
In the literature it speaks of sparking a transformation

55:53.320 --> 55:55.880
and phases like that.

55:56.240 --> 56:00.520
This implies that You can do the job? He is asking whether

56:00.720 --> 56:03.680
there are others who can do the job,

56:03.880 --> 56:07.400
of doing this, of achieving this result?

56:07.680 --> 56:12.680
Now I must say, I must confess, I haven't met any who does en-masse,

56:12.880 --> 56:16.040
I haven't met. I mean, I wish I could meet someone

56:16.240 --> 56:18.400
because I would like to retire now. I'm sixty years of age,

56:18.720 --> 56:20.360
so I better retire now, isn't it?

56:20.600 --> 56:23.160
But the trouble is, I haven't met anyone so far,

56:23.360 --> 56:25.280
who can give a en-masse Realization.

56:25.480 --> 56:29.880
Also My disciples, can give Realization to people,

56:30.120 --> 56:32.800
but not en-masse, they have to use My photograph or something.

56:33.000 --> 56:36.160
So, if you know of anyone, I'll be very happy to know someone

56:36.360 --> 56:39.480
but I haven't met any. So, I don't claim I'm the only one,

56:39.680 --> 56:43.080
could be many, but I haven't met anyone, I'm sorry to say.

56:43.280 --> 56:47.880
I'm thinking of people like Muktananda and Maharishi.

56:48.200 --> 56:53.040
You must go, that's, that's the ashram he has been to, I was saying.

56:53.240 --> 56:55.280
That's the ashram he has been to.

56:55.800 --> 56:58.840
Y - And also Maharishi.
Dr. Warren - And Maharishi he is saying.

56:59.040 --> 57:03.000
We have patients from there, epilepsy, I'll show you, you meet them.

57:03.200 --> 57:05.120
They are epileptic patients who are coming to Me.

57:05.360 --> 57:08.680
He has made sixty, six thousand crores of rupees.

57:08.880 --> 57:12.440
Crores. It's in billions and billions of money.

57:12.680 --> 57:15.200
You must meet the people who have suffered from there.

57:15.400 --> 57:17.360
If you think so, it's all right.

57:17.600 --> 57:19.680
You can go to them, but then don't come back to Me,

57:19.880 --> 57:21.400
that's the only thing is, because

57:21.600 --> 57:24.320
I know they end up with epilepsy, penniless

57:24.520 --> 57:28.080
and all kinds of problems are there.

57:28.880 --> 57:32.120
Muktananda, recently I heard in Delhi

57:32.320 --> 57:34.880
that his two disciples are now fighting

57:35.080 --> 57:37.680
for the seat and third lady has now got over

57:37.880 --> 57:40.280
but there's a problem of

57:40.480 --> 57:43.400
diamonds worth thirty-four million rupees,

57:43.600 --> 57:45.880
of diamonds they are fighting among themselves.

57:46.080 --> 57:48.000
This is all right. I'll do it. You see, if you move,

57:48.200 --> 57:51.280
all the people start looking at you. Please don't come.

57:51.880 --> 57:55.200
Yes. All right? Thank you.

57:55.600 --> 57:58.800
So, that's not the way. You should see the result on people.

57:59.000 --> 58:00.880
That's the thing, on yourself.

58:01.120 --> 58:03.720
You see, they have lot of money, they have made lot of money

58:03.920 --> 58:05.760
and they can propagate whatever they like

58:05.960 --> 58:11.880
but you must see what you get yourself, is the point.

58:15.880 --> 58:18.680
Mataji I'm very grateful that You pointed out

58:18.880 --> 58:21.960
that the individual mind can't be trusted.

58:22.160 --> 58:24.760
On the other hand the collective mind can be,

58:24.960 --> 58:26.680
and I'd like to thank You for that.

58:26.880 --> 58:31.960
And by the way I'm the gentleman that Mataji [corrected].

58:32.600 --> 58:35.680
I came from Perth

58:35.880 --> 58:39.040
and on the sixth occasion tried to feel

58:39.240 --> 58:42.920
the breeze on the top of my head, I really didn't. Disgusted by,

58:43.120 --> 58:46.200
I've also been to Krishnamurti in England.

58:46.520 --> 58:48.400
And he's been to all of them.

58:48.840 --> 58:52.920
And not to mention, not to mention [unclear] this to this night.

58:53.120 --> 58:57.680
And on the second occasion in Perth I did feel the breeze

58:57.880 --> 59:00.880
on the top of the head, so...

59:01.280 --> 59:03.720
Thank you. I was so happy to see him here

59:03.920 --> 59:07.240
because once, when I met him, he's such a great seeker, you see,

59:07.480 --> 59:10.480
really tears came into My eyes. I said look at this one

59:10.720 --> 59:14.680
he's such a great seeker and I don't know what has happened to him.

59:14.880 --> 59:17.280
And today I find him here. I'm so very happy, you don't know.

59:17.480 --> 59:20.680
It's such a great thing, because you are seeking the truth.

59:20.880 --> 59:22.400
You are My children I feel.

59:22.640 --> 59:27.120
The way you are mislaid is something so painful, you can't imagine.

59:27.320 --> 59:30.680
It's very painful.

59:30.880 --> 59:33.680
Yes, please.

59:33.880 --> 59:37.680
Mataji, what [do You think] of the aboriginals' life from Australia?

59:37.880 --> 59:40.680
You see, the only problem with aboriginals' [rights],

59:40.880 --> 59:45.800
[unclear]

59:46.000 --> 59:48.680
You just tell Me.

59:48.880 --> 59:53.400
He's, he's concerned about the aboriginal problem and

59:53.600 --> 59:55.680
No, they all can get Realization very fast,

59:55.880 --> 59:57.840
much faster than you people can.

59:58.040 --> 01:00:00.320
I've given Realization to some of aboriginal people

01:00:00.760 --> 01:00:02.400
because they are very simple people you know.

01:00:02.600 --> 01:00:04.160
They are extremely simple, good people,

01:00:04.360 --> 01:00:06.680
they get Realization in no time. You just don't worry,

01:00:06.880 --> 01:00:09.280
I'm going to look after them very well.

01:00:09.520 --> 01:00:11.640
May God bless you, you are concerned about them,

01:00:11.840 --> 01:00:15.400
I'm very happy to know. Yes.

01:00:16.880 --> 01:00:17.960
Shall we have it?

01:00:18.160 --> 01:00:21.880
Now is there any one else?

01:00:22.440 --> 01:00:26.800
Now one thing is, you should not in any way feel diffident.

01:00:27.000 --> 01:00:30.200
That's one thing is very important.

01:00:30.440 --> 01:00:35.080
As I said that you are all children of God.

01:00:35.320 --> 01:00:38.760
As William Blake has said that

01:00:38.960 --> 01:00:44.400
man of God will become prophet, they'll become prophets,

01:00:44.640 --> 01:00:47.400
and they will have powers to make other prophets.

01:00:47.640 --> 01:00:50.120
The time has come, that's what is the time.

01:00:50.400 --> 01:00:52.720
So, don't feel diffident about anything,

01:00:52.920 --> 01:00:55.680
by no means, nor you should feel guilty.

01:00:55.880 --> 01:00:57.680
That's a very big disease in the West,

01:00:57.880 --> 01:01:00.200
to feel guilty for nothing at all.

01:01:00.400 --> 01:01:04.880
God is great love so please, don't feel guilty.

01:01:05.120 --> 01:01:08.040
These two first conditions has to be there,

01:01:08.240 --> 01:01:12.280
that you are not to feel guilty, upset. Be cheerful

01:01:12.480 --> 01:01:15.800
that you have to enter into the Kingdom of God, that's your right.

01:01:16.000 --> 01:01:18.680
As seekers of truth you have greatest right

01:01:18.880 --> 01:01:20.680
than anybody else has.

01:01:20.880 --> 01:01:22.200
So please don't feel guilty

01:01:22.400 --> 01:01:24.680
for whatever you have done. Is finished now.

01:01:24.880 --> 01:01:27.200
Now is not what you have done,

01:01:27.400 --> 01:01:31.200
but what you are going to be. So may God bless you!

01:01:31.400 --> 01:01:35.400
Let us have the

01:01:35.680 --> 01:01:38.000
session of Self Realization, for which

01:01:38.200 --> 01:01:42.800
simple things you have to do, is to take out your shoes.

01:01:43.920 --> 01:01:47.040
It's a very simple thing that one should take out one's shoes.

01:01:47.240 --> 01:01:50.680
It's good because the Mother Earth helps us a lot

01:01:50.880 --> 01:01:53.920
by taking out the shoes.

01:02:12.520 --> 01:02:15.680
Now put both your feet

01:02:15.880 --> 01:02:20.320
on the Mother Earth, parallel,

01:02:25.880 --> 01:02:30.280
and put both the hands towards Me, like this,

01:02:32.280 --> 01:02:34.360
or on your lap. Be comfortable,

01:02:34.560 --> 01:02:36.920
that's the main point, is you have to be comfortable.

01:02:37.120 --> 01:02:40.880
If there's any thing tight on your waist or anything,

01:02:41.080 --> 01:02:45.880
please try to loosen it.

01:02:46.160 --> 01:02:50.880
Put your both the hands straight

01:02:53.560 --> 01:02:56.680
and close your eyes. Please close your eyes.

01:02:56.880 --> 01:03:00.280
You are not to open your eyes till I tell you.

01:03:00.640 --> 01:03:05.680
Because when the Kundalini rises above this Agnya Chakra,

01:03:05.880 --> 01:03:10.960
your eyes, if they are not closed, will stop at that point.

01:03:11.200 --> 01:03:14.120
It will be nice if you can take out your spectacles also

01:03:14.320 --> 01:03:16.920
because eye-sight is very much benefited

01:03:17.120 --> 01:03:20.160
by Kundalini rising.

01:03:20.400 --> 01:03:26.080
So just put both your hands towards Me, very comfortably,

01:03:26.320 --> 01:03:28.520
and don't worry if you are thinking

01:03:28.720 --> 01:03:32.800
or your mind is going here and there. Do not try to concentrate.

01:03:33.000 --> 01:03:35.400
It will just work out, by itself.

01:03:35.600 --> 01:03:37.680
You don't have to do anything. it's all within you,

01:03:37.880 --> 01:03:40.680
it will just work out.

01:03:40.880 --> 01:03:43.120
When I will tell you what is to be done, when I find

01:03:43.320 --> 01:03:46.920
there's a problem in a particular chakra in the collective way,

01:03:47.120 --> 01:03:49.240
then I will tell you and that's how you should follow.

01:03:49.440 --> 01:03:51.400
But just now, for the time being,

01:03:51.720 --> 01:03:54.040
you just sit with both the hands on your lap,

01:03:54.240 --> 01:03:57.040
fingers towards Me and close your eyes please.

01:03:57.240 --> 01:03:59.680
Have full faith in yourself, first of all,

01:03:59.880 --> 01:04:04.320
that you are the children of God

01:04:04.680 --> 01:04:08.560
and that He is your Father who is waiting for you.

01:04:08.760 --> 01:04:12.200
He's anxious that you should enter into His Kingdom

01:04:12.400 --> 01:04:18.040
so that He bestows all the beauty and bounties.

01:04:44.000 --> 01:04:47.880
Now, your right hand is the hand of action,

01:04:48.080 --> 01:04:51.960
and left hand is the hand of your desire.

01:04:52.160 --> 01:04:55.120
Your desire is to be the Spirit.

01:04:55.320 --> 01:04:58.320
So put your left hand where it is

01:04:58.640 --> 01:05:00.680
in a proper way, in a comfortable way.

01:05:00.880 --> 01:05:05.600
You don't have to move the left hand, because the desire is there

01:05:05.800 --> 01:05:09.240
but action has to take place through the right hand.

01:05:09.480 --> 01:05:12.200
Now, keep the left hand as it is

01:05:12.400 --> 01:05:15.880
and the right hand, you put it on your heart to begin with.

01:05:16.080 --> 01:05:18.680
On your heart, on the left hand side, please,

01:05:18.880 --> 01:05:24.040
and with a very humble feeling

01:05:24.240 --> 01:05:28.240
ask the question, "Mother, am I the Spirit?"

01:05:28.480 --> 01:05:33.960
Ask this question three times please, "Mother, am I the Spirit?"

01:05:56.160 --> 01:06:01.360
Now put the same hand, down on the stomach, on the left hand side.

01:06:01.720 --> 01:06:04.400
We have to work only on the left side, with the right hand.

01:06:04.640 --> 01:06:06.680
Press there with your finger

01:06:06.880 --> 01:06:11.120
and just say with full confidence,

01:06:11.320 --> 01:06:17.240
"Mother, I am my own master, I am my own guru."

01:06:33.600 --> 01:06:38.880
This is to awaken your own principle of guru.

01:06:39.120 --> 01:06:42.680
If you have believed in all gurus, forget it for the time being.

01:06:42.880 --> 01:06:45.360
First you become your own guru, then you will know

01:06:45.680 --> 01:06:49.800
whether your guru is true or not.

01:07:02.520 --> 01:07:04.880
You have to say this ten times, that,

01:07:05.080 --> 01:07:10.400
"Mother, I am my own guru", with full confidence.

01:07:22.880 --> 01:07:26.160
On the Kundalini itself.

01:07:47.760 --> 01:07:52.760
Now, raise this hand higher again, onto the heart.

01:07:52.960 --> 01:07:57.720
Now with full confidence and humility

01:07:57.920 --> 01:08:01.720
you have to say twelve times, "Mother, I am the Spirit".

01:08:01.920 --> 01:08:05.200
Why these times I am saying? Because of the different plexuses,

01:08:05.400 --> 01:08:09.800
the number of plexuses, you have on these centers.

01:08:10.000 --> 01:08:15.960
Twelve times please say, "Mother, I am the Spirit".

01:08:18.880 --> 01:08:21.160
Heart.

01:09:02.120 --> 01:09:06.600
Now, the same hand you have to raise higher

01:09:06.800 --> 01:09:09.680
onto the left side of your neck. This is another center

01:09:09.880 --> 01:09:12.880
which is called as Vishuddhi center.

01:09:13.080 --> 01:09:16.640
Here you have to say, "Mother, I'm not guilty".

01:09:16.840 --> 01:09:22.360
This is to be said sixteen times as a punishment for feeling guilty.

01:09:22.880 --> 01:09:26.040
You have to be cheerful and not to be upset about anything.

01:09:26.240 --> 01:09:28.640
Just say, "Mother, I am not guilty", just say that,

01:09:28.840 --> 01:09:32.320
"for doing anything". Because you are seekers of God,

01:09:32.640 --> 01:09:35.720
and if you have done any mistakes, it is done of your [ignorance],

01:09:35.920 --> 01:09:37.640
none of your mistakes.

01:09:37.840 --> 01:09:43.160
It's just done, because you did not know what was to be done.

01:09:44.480 --> 01:09:49.800
So just first of all forgive yourself and...

01:10:19.680 --> 01:10:22.680
Now put the same hand on your forehead across,

01:10:22.880 --> 01:10:26.880
on your forehead across.

01:10:29.240 --> 01:10:35.160
Now say one thing, which is very simple,

01:10:35.720 --> 01:10:41.400
"Mother, I forgive everyone". Say it from your heart, everyone.

01:10:41.600 --> 01:10:46.680
Some might think that it is difficult to forgive, but it is a myth.

01:10:46.880 --> 01:10:49.920
By not forgiving you are doing no harm to the other person,

01:10:50.120 --> 01:10:52.240
you are just harming yourself.

01:10:52.480 --> 01:10:57.000
So just say, "Mother, I forgive everyone".

01:11:22.360 --> 01:11:26.880
Unless and until you forgive others, why should God forgive you?

01:11:27.120 --> 01:11:30.360
Just say it with full heart. Put your hand on your forehead,

01:11:30.720 --> 01:11:34.240
comfortably, and say, "Mother, I forgive everyone".

01:11:34.440 --> 01:11:36.760
From your heart, just forgive everything.

01:11:36.960 --> 01:11:40.600
You'll find your load and stress will all go away.

01:11:40.840 --> 01:11:44.600
This is a mantra for that center.

01:11:44.960 --> 01:11:47.680
Now raise your hand on top of your head

01:11:47.880 --> 01:11:53.040
and just press in the center, in the fontanel bone area.

01:12:02.320 --> 01:12:06.120
At this point, I cannot go further.

01:12:06.320 --> 01:12:08.480
You have to give Me a consent.

01:12:08.680 --> 01:12:10.760
You have to ask for your Realization

01:12:10.960 --> 01:12:12.880
because you are free to choose.

01:12:13.120 --> 01:12:14.720
With your heart you should say, "Mother,

01:12:14.920 --> 01:12:20.800
please give me Realization". Just ask for it.

01:12:28.080 --> 01:12:30.680
Seven times, and slowly raise your hand

01:12:30.880 --> 01:12:33.560
and see if there's a breeze, cool breeze coming in.

01:12:33.760 --> 01:12:37.560
First, you might feel the heat coming out.

01:12:41.880 --> 01:12:45.880
Raise it higher, about four inches maybe.

01:12:46.160 --> 01:12:50.520
Just see if there is... You can move your hand and see.

01:12:50.800 --> 01:12:53.640
You can put another hand on top of your head

01:12:53.840 --> 01:12:56.840
and the right hand down, the same way as the left hand was.

01:12:57.040 --> 01:12:58.400
So you can change your hand

01:12:58.680 --> 01:13:02.560
and see if there's a cool breeze coming in.

01:13:11.200 --> 01:13:13.400
Gives some shock.

01:13:52.880 --> 01:13:55.200
This gives a shock in.

01:14:19.400 --> 01:14:22.080
Just try to see if there's a cool breeze.

01:14:22.280 --> 01:14:27.080
Again. Raise your hand one by one.

01:14:36.720 --> 01:14:42.000
Good! Those who are feeling, please raise your hands.

01:14:42.320 --> 01:14:45.120
Great! So many of you.

01:14:45.320 --> 01:14:47.680
Now you can open your eyes and raise your hands,

01:14:47.880 --> 01:14:50.120
both the hands like this. Let's see.

01:14:50.360 --> 01:14:53.680
And ask the question, "Mother, is this the Brahma shakti?"

01:14:53.880 --> 01:14:57.840
"Is this the power of God, that is all-pervading love?"

01:14:58.040 --> 01:15:02.960
"Is this the breeze of the Holy Ghost?" Ask a question.

01:15:16.160 --> 01:15:18.760
It's a sensation in the fingers you feel first

01:15:18.960 --> 01:15:22.000
and a kind of cool breeze all around.

01:15:22.200 --> 01:15:24.160
Now bring your hands down and see if it is coming

01:15:24.360 --> 01:15:27.720
in your hands as well.

01:15:32.320 --> 01:15:37.240
You'll feel very peaceful, extremely peaceful.

01:15:38.320 --> 01:15:40.880
Better.

01:15:43.960 --> 01:15:46.880
Good?

01:15:48.880 --> 01:15:52.280
Close your eyes and enjoy yourself.

01:16:20.800 --> 01:16:23.120
It's better.

01:16:25.160 --> 01:16:27.920
Now I will teach you how to raise your own Kundalini,

01:16:28.120 --> 01:16:29.640
if you can open your eyes.

01:16:29.840 --> 01:16:33.040
This will even help you to feel it more, if you have not felt

01:16:33.240 --> 01:16:36.520
because it's a very subtle, sukshma,

01:16:36.720 --> 01:16:39.080
and you, we are from a gross awareness going

01:16:39.280 --> 01:16:42.840
to the sukshma's awareness, to the subtle awareness.

01:16:43.040 --> 01:16:46.360
It is rather difficult in the beginning to conceive it,

01:16:46.680 --> 01:16:49.680
because you cannot conceive it mentally, you have to feel it.

01:16:49.880 --> 01:16:52.360
And unless and until you have felt it you should not

01:16:52.640 --> 01:16:56.640
say that you have felt it, but try to understand that it is there.

01:16:56.880 --> 01:16:57.960
It is there.

01:16:58.160 --> 01:17:01.000
Now let us see how you can all raise your own Kundalini.

01:17:01.200 --> 01:17:04.360
You don't have to go to any guru to do it. Yourself can do it.

01:17:04.640 --> 01:17:09.880
Put your left hand in front of your Kundalini,

01:17:10.080 --> 01:17:13.240
just while you are sitting, just in front, little further,

01:17:13.520 --> 01:17:15.760
because you have to move the other hand like this.

01:17:15.960 --> 01:17:19.680
You have to move the other hand which is the power of action,

01:17:19.880 --> 01:17:23.360
up, front, below, backwards.

01:17:23.640 --> 01:17:26.680
Up, front, below, backwards. Like that you have to move.

01:17:26.880 --> 01:17:29.400
So you have to start raising it now from that point.

01:17:29.680 --> 01:17:32.600
Let's start moving it

01:17:32.840 --> 01:17:35.840
up, front, below, backwards.

01:17:36.040 --> 01:17:38.280
Start moving it, trying to raise this hand.

01:17:38.560 --> 01:17:41.200
Bring it up higher, higher, higher, higher.

01:17:41.400 --> 01:17:44.680
Now put up your hands absolutely and give it a big twist there.

01:17:44.880 --> 01:17:48.720
Twist and now tie it up.

01:17:48.960 --> 01:17:53.320
Let's do it once more, again.

01:17:59.520 --> 01:18:03.160
We have to do it three times, for three powers. Now again tie it.

01:18:03.400 --> 01:18:04.880
If you don't try it and if you fail,

01:18:05.080 --> 01:18:08.200
then you should not blame Me for that.

01:18:08.480 --> 01:18:11.360
Again try it. Worth trying and finding out if it is true or not.

01:18:11.600 --> 01:18:14.960
Come along let's have it again.

01:18:16.360 --> 01:18:20.960
This time we have to give three twists and three knots.

01:18:21.320 --> 01:18:27.240
Now give one twist, one, another twist,

01:18:28.680 --> 01:18:31.960
the third one and knot it out.

01:18:32.160 --> 01:18:35.240
Now see your hands.

01:18:44.520 --> 01:18:47.560
Working out?

01:18:51.160 --> 01:18:55.360
Some people are getting more in the left, some more on the right.

01:18:55.680 --> 01:18:59.520
How to correct it, also one should know.

01:18:59.760 --> 01:19:04.680
Those who are getting more on the left and less on the right,

01:19:04.880 --> 01:19:09.040
should put right hand towards Me like this

01:19:09.280 --> 01:19:13.560
The one which is less should be towards Me,

01:19:13.760 --> 01:19:17.360
and the left hand on the stomach.

01:19:19.960 --> 01:19:22.400
If the right hand is getting less,

01:19:22.640 --> 01:19:25.400
then put the right hand towards Me and the left hand in the stomach

01:19:25.640 --> 01:19:29.880
means something wrong with your guru principle

01:19:30.080 --> 01:19:33.600
or maybe with your liver or kidney

01:19:33.800 --> 01:19:37.680
or anything like that, stomach part.

01:19:39.080 --> 01:19:41.480
Those who are getting

01:19:41.680 --> 01:19:45.680
less on the left hand side or not at all on the left hand side

01:19:45.880 --> 01:19:49.880
should put left hand towards Me and right hand on the heart.

01:19:50.120 --> 01:19:53.400
Is only thing you should know how to understand your own machine,

01:19:53.640 --> 01:19:57.040
Left hand towards Me and right hand on the heart.

01:19:57.720 --> 01:20:01.160
Those people who are getting less on the left hand side

01:20:01.360 --> 01:20:07.120
should put the left hand like this and the right hand on the heart.

01:20:10.640 --> 01:20:14.960
So many are still feeling guilty. Please don't feel guilty.

01:20:15.240 --> 01:20:18.080
Still feeling guilty I can catch on the left Vishuddhi,

01:20:18.280 --> 01:20:19.680
means feeling guilty for nothing at all.

01:20:19.880 --> 01:20:22.280
Why are you feeling guilty for anything?

01:20:22.520 --> 01:20:24.760
We have to talk about the present and not about the past

01:20:24.960 --> 01:20:28.840
because past doesn't exist.

01:20:30.320 --> 01:20:32.920
Better!

01:20:36.480 --> 01:20:40.200
Now put both the hands and see how it works out.

01:20:57.520 --> 01:21:02.880
Watch Me without thinking, just without thinking.

01:21:18.720 --> 01:21:20.000
It's feeling it?

01:21:20.200 --> 01:21:22.360
All those who are feeling cool breeze in the hand

01:21:22.600 --> 01:21:26.560
or in the head, raise your hands please, again.

01:21:29.400 --> 01:21:31.880
You all didn't feel at all, anyway?

01:21:32.080 --> 01:21:34.120
None of you?

01:21:34.320 --> 01:21:36.600
All right.

01:21:36.840 --> 01:21:40.280
It's good, lots of people have felt it.

01:21:40.880 --> 01:21:43.600
Say it again. Say again, they got confused.

01:21:43.840 --> 01:21:46.880
Yes. Those who have felt the cool breeze in the hand

01:21:47.080 --> 01:21:51.000
or on the head, please raise your hands.

01:21:56.640 --> 01:21:58.680
All right!

01:21:58.880 --> 01:22:02.880
Now those who have not felt, can also feel it.

01:22:03.120 --> 01:22:06.000
Nothing to be desperate or unhappy.

01:22:06.200 --> 01:22:09.120
Maybe something wrong with you physically, mentally,

01:22:09.320 --> 01:22:12.560
maybe something wrong somewhere which can be found out.

01:22:12.800 --> 01:22:15.520
It's not difficult to find out. It's very simple.

01:22:15.760 --> 01:22:21.720
So, tomorrow if you can come again,

01:22:22.040 --> 01:22:25.040
I'll work it out for you, very nicely,

01:22:25.240 --> 01:22:28.240
and also for people who have felt it,

01:22:28.480 --> 01:22:30.640
they should understand that it is to be retained.

01:22:30.840 --> 01:22:33.480
You cannot think about it. By thinking you did not get it,

01:22:33.680 --> 01:22:38.560
it just happened. So to retain it, what is to be done?

01:22:38.760 --> 01:22:40.720
You can take from them the books.

01:22:40.920 --> 01:22:43.600
Those who have got it, can take the books from them,

01:22:43.840 --> 01:22:46.080
and can work it out tonight.

01:22:46.280 --> 01:22:49.600
But don't read the book, otherwise you will again start thinking.

01:22:49.800 --> 01:22:52.680
It's better not to read much about things and

01:22:52.880 --> 01:22:54.640
as long as you do not think about it.

01:22:54.840 --> 01:22:59.680
Just give peace to your head, which has been thinking all the while.

01:22:59.880 --> 01:23:03.000
So allow it to rest for a while.

01:23:03.200 --> 01:23:07.080
Those who haven't felt it can go at the back and some people

01:23:07.280 --> 01:23:10.080
who can work on them can find out.

01:23:10.280 --> 01:23:13.000
Tomorrow I'll personally see you, each one of you

01:23:13.200 --> 01:23:15.360
and we'll work it out, in a better way.

01:23:15.600 --> 01:23:18.080
We have to establish it, fully. Tomorrow I'll come down

01:23:18.280 --> 01:23:22.280
and see all of you, one by one. May God bless you!

01:23:22.600 --> 01:23:24.880
But those who want, can go at the back, please.

01:23:25.120 --> 01:23:26.640
They are there, they'll just look, see,

01:23:26.840 --> 01:23:31.400
tell you what's the problem is. All right? It's very simple.

01:23:33.320 --> 01:23:35.320
Vishuddhi.

01:23:37.440 --> 01:23:40.080
I hope tomorrow you bring some more friends of yours,

01:23:40.280 --> 01:23:44.280
to tell them, telephone to them, that they should come to reality.

01:23:44.520 --> 01:23:47.520
Thank you very much.

