01:24:19.400 --> 01:24:21.760
developing your Self Realization.

01:24:22.000 --> 01:24:23.920
So even if you haven't felt it tonight, don't,

01:24:24.120 --> 01:24:26.160
as She said, be desperate about it.

01:24:26.400 --> 01:24:29.480
We, we switched the air conditioning off, so that

01:24:29.680 --> 01:24:34.000
