01:24:34.240 --> 01:24:37.320
It is, again She says, "Don't be desperate,

01:24:37.520 --> 01:24:39.320
don't be anxious that it didn't happen.

01:24:39.520 --> 01:24:42.400
It doesn't mean that you are not a spiritual person.

01:24:42.640 --> 01:24:44.600
Maybe the perception is a little bit dulled..

01:24:44.800 --> 01:24:47.240
S.M.: Don't doubt yourself, that's the thing.

